      • retrieveStorageTube

        public Storage retrieveStorageTube(String barcode)
                            throws DAOException
        Retrieves Storage object representing a tube. The 2D barcode for a tube is unique across plates so this method is expected to return a single results. Compare to wells in 96 well plate that have same type and index across multiple plates
        Parameters:
        barcode - unique identifier for storage tube
        Returns:
        retrieved Storage
        Throws:
        DAOException - on exception

        public Storage getLocation(Storage scheme,
